quran[9{c,v,t}:
21,82,aur shyatin mein se hum ne aisay bohat soon ko is ka tabay bana diya tha jo is ke liye ghote lagatay aur is ke siwa doosray kaam karte thay un sab ke nigran hum hi thay
21,83,"aur yahi ( hosh mandi aur hukum o ilm ki Nemat ) hum ne ayub ko di thi yaad karo, jabkay is ne apne rab ko puraka ke"" mujhe bemari lag gayi hai aur to Arhamhai """
21,84,"hum ne is ki dua qubool ki aur jo takleef ussay thi is ko door kar diya, aur sirf is ke ahal o Ayal hi is ko nahi diye balkay un ke sath itnay hi aur bhi diye, apni khaas rehmat ke tor par, aur is liye ke yeh aik sabaq ho ibadat guzaron ke liye"
21,85,aur yahi Nemat Ismael aur Adrees aur ZULKAFFAL ko di ke yeh sab sabir log thay
21,86,aur un ko hum ne apni rehmat mein daakhil kya ke woh salhoon mein se thay
21,87,"aur machhli walay ko bhi hum ne nawaza yaad karo jabkay woh baggar kar chala gaya tha aur samgha tha ke hum is par girift nah karen ge aakhir ko uss ne tarikeon mein puraka"" nahi hai koi khuda magar too, pak hai teri zaat, be shak mein ne qasoor kya """
21,88,"tab hum ne is ki dua qubool ki aur gham se is ko nijaat bakhsh, aur isi terhan hum mominon ko bacha liya karte hain"
21,89,"aur Zikria ko, jabkay is ne apne rab ko puraka ke"" ae parvar-digaar, mujhe akela nah chore, aur behtareen waris to too hi hai """
21,90,"pas hum ne is ki dua qubool ki aur usay yahya ataa kya aur is ki biwi ko is ke liye durust kar diya yeh log neki ke kamon mein daud dhoop karte thay aur hamein raghbat aur khauf ke sath pukarte thay, aur hamaray agay jhuke hue thay"
